  "displayName": "Readback - Add Info During Confirmation",
  "description": "User provides special requests alongside their time selection. The requests are deferred (BookReservation input) while the time gets immediate readback. After name is collected, the deferred group (name + requests) fires a combined readback that includes the allergy info from earlier. Verifies that unsolicited info added mid-flow is preserved through deferred routing.",
